    <entry>
      <title>Hexo文章中插入视频音乐</title>
      <link href="/2020/01/30/Hexo%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E4%B8%AD%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90/"/>
      <url>/2020/01/30/Hexo%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E4%B8%AD%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><p>利用<code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code> <strong>HTML内联框架元素 </strong> 表示嵌套的browsing context。它能够将另一个HTML页面嵌入到当前页面中。</p><a id="more"></a><p>不用担心Markdown渲染器，Hexo的渲染器直接原封不动渲染HTNL代码。 能否实现要看视频平台有没有站外代码生成。</p><h1 id="代码嵌入">代码嵌入</h1><h2 id="嵌入音乐">嵌入音乐</h2><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="330" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&amp;id=1375725396&amp;auto=0&amp;height=66"></iframe><p>在网易云的音乐图片下面<em>生成外链播放器</em>然后就可以设置生成了，注意他说是iframe插件，不用主动去安装它，直接把代码复制到文章中就可以用了。</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">不用担心Markdown渲染器，Hexo的渲染器直接原封不动渲染HTNL代码。</span><br><span class="line">能否实现要看视频平台有没有站外代码生成。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 嵌入音乐</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;iframe <span class="attribute">frameborder</span>=<span class="string">"no"</span> <span class="attribute">border</span>=<span class="string">"0"</span> <span class="attribute">marginwidth</span>=<span class="string">"0"</span> <span class="attribute">marginheight</span>=<span class="string">"0"</span> <span class="attribute">width</span>=330 <span class="attribute">height</span>=86 <span class="attribute">src</span>=<span class="string">"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&amp;id=1375725396&amp;auto=0&amp;height=66"</span>&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">在网易云的音乐图片下面*生成外链播放器*然后就可以设置生成了，注意他说是iframe插件，不用主动去安装它，直接把代码复制到文章中就可以用了。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="嵌入视频">嵌入视频</h2><p>方法和嵌入音乐一样，在B站视频下面点击分享图标，有嵌入代码的框，复制就可以了。 注意，视频只有360p的画质，选择更高画质会跳到主站，</p><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=83764451&amp;cid=143294804&amp;page=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe><h1 id="插件嵌入">插件嵌入</h1><p>未完待续。。。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Bolg </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Markdown </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Markdown语法</title>
      <link href="/2020/01/29/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>/2020/01/29/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><p>Markdown是一种<strong>轻量级标记语言</strong>，它允许人们“使用易读易写的纯文本格式编写文档，然后转换成有效的XHTML或者HTML文档”。这种语言吸收了很多在电子邮件中已有的纯文本标记的特性。</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="标题">标题</h2><figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 一级</span><br><span class="line">## 二级</span><br><span class="line">### 三级</span><br><span class="line">......</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="段落">段落</h2><p>结尾加两个空格换行</p><h2 id="字体">字体</h2><p><em>text</em><br><strong>text</strong><br><strong><em>text</em></strong></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*倾斜*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">_斜体_</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**粗体**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">__粗体__</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">***粗斜**</span>*</span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">___粗斜__</span>_</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>##分割线</p><hr><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">***</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span><span class="bullet">* *</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">*****</span><span class="strong">*****</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>- -</span><br><span class="line">------</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="删除线">删除线</h2><p><del>text</del></p><figure class="highlight applescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~<span class="built_in">text</span>~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="下划线">下划线</h2><p><u>text</u></p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span>text<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="脚注">脚注</h2><p><a href="#fn1" class="footnote-ref" id="fnref1" role="doc-noteref"><sup>1</sup></a></p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">示例<span class="selector-attr">[^hhhh]</span>.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-attr">[^hhhh]</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:hello</span> <span class="selector-tag">world</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="列表">列表</h2><ul><li>one</li><li>tow</li><li>three</li></ul><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>one</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>tow</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>three</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+ </span>one</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+ </span>tow</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+ </span>three</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>one</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>tow</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>three</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="有序列表">有序列表</h2><ol type="1"><li>one</li><li>tow</li><li>three</li></ol><figure class="highlight angelscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">1.</span> one</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2.</span> tow</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">3.</span> three</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="列表嵌套">列表嵌套</h2><ol type="1"><li>A<ul><li>hh</li><li>jj</li></ul></li><li>B<ol type="1"><li>hh</li><li>kkk</li></ol></li></ol><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>A</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>hh</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>jj</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>B</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>hh</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>kkk</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="区块">区块</h2><blockquote><p>one</p><blockquote><p>tow</p><blockquote><p>three</p></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;one</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;</span>tow</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;</span>&gt;three</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><h1 id="hhh">hhh</h1><ul><li>hh</li></ul></blockquote><ul><li><p>hh</p><blockquote><p>hh hhh</p></blockquote></li><li><p>h</p></li></ul><h2 id="代码">代码</h2><p><code>printf()</code></p><figure class="highlight arcade"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">`printf()`</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>int main(){printf(&quot;hello world&quot;);}制表符（Tab）和<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 链接</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">github</span>](<span class="link">https://github.com/explore</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">https:</span>//<span class="attr">github.com</span>/<span class="attr">explore</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre><p><a href="https://github.com/explore" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github</a> <a href="https://github.com/explore" class="uri" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/explore</a> <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>链接也可以用变量来代替，文档末尾附带变量地址： 这个链接用 1 作为网址变量 <a href="http://www.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google</a> 这个链接用 runoob 作为网址变量 <a href="http://www.runoob.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Runoob</a> 然后在文档的结尾为变量赋值（网址）</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 图片  </span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">hhh 图片</span>](<span class="link">http://www.umfk.edu/default/cache/file/05D2B8D5-54CC-4A38-B59D06DF660577C3_librarypagebg.jpg</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"http://www.umfk.edu/default/cache/file/05D2B8D5-54CC-4A38-B59D06DF660577C3_librarypagebg.jpg"</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">"50%"</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure><img src="http://www.umfk.edu/default/cache/file/05D2B8D5-54CC-4A38-B59D06DF660577C3_librarypagebg.jpg" alt><figcaption>hhh 图片</figcaption></figure><p><img src="http://www.umfk.edu/default/cache/file/05D2B8D5-54CC-4A38-B59D06DF660577C3_librarypagebg.jpg" width="50%"> <figure class="highlight gherkin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 表格</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string"> 1    </span>|<span class="string">    2 </span>|<span class="string">  3   </span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string"> :--- </span>|<span class="string"> ---: </span>|<span class="string"> :--: </span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string"> 11   </span>|<span class="string">   22 </span>|<span class="string">  33  </span>|</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><table><thead><tr class="header"><th style="text-align: left;">1</th><th style="text-align: right;">2</th><th style="text-align: center;">3</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: left;">11</td><td style="text-align: right;">22</td><td style="text-align: center;">33</td></tr></tbody></table><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">## HTML元素</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">&lt;kbd&gt;</span>Ctrl<span class="params">&lt;/kbd&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><kbd>Ctrl</kbd> <kbd> <b> <i> <em> <sup> <sub> <br>等 <figure class="highlight taggerscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">## 转义</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">\*</span><span class="symbol">\*</span> hhhh <span class="symbol">\*</span><span class="symbol">\*</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></sub></sup></em></i></b></kbd></p><p>** hhhh ** ```</p><section class="footnotes" role="doc-endnotes"><hr><ol><li id="fn1" role="doc-endnote"><p>hello world<a href="#fnref1" class="footnote-back" role="doc-backlink">↩︎</a></p></li></ol></section>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 标记语言 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Markdown </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
